      "updated": 1775334275199,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Regressions:\n\nLike when you have something working .. but then you apply some changes or improvements \nbut it regresses back to some broken state ..",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Regressions:\n\nLike when you have something working .. but then you apply some changes or improvements \nbut it regresses back to some broken state ..",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YMsoONfgOHDwKj6PfOcks",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 629.7492465652933,
      "y": 2136.941237265741,
      "width": 1001.28403384483,
