    },
    {
      "id": "BaJCv9qdQ5z3N2Qxqk8GL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -6153.092810659489,
      "y": 885.0957583358562,
      "width": 681.9991455078125,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1425037101,
      "version": 644,
      "versionNonce": 1236330149,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775334275199,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "DOUBLE FAULT:\n\n- This happens when you run into some error when calling the \nthe exception handler of a function. Something like an\nexception occurs when handling another exception.\n\n- It can be something like you encountered a page fault,\nbut when dealing with it .. you run into some problem with \nthe stack.. \n\n\nTRIPLE FAULT:\n\n- This is some error that occurs when handling a double fault.\n- it is unrecoverable ...\n- leads to a complete hardware reset!",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "DOUBLE FAULT:\n\n- This happens when you run into some error when calling the \nthe exception handler of a function. Something like an\nexception occurs when handling another exception.\n\n- It can be something like you encountered a page fault,\nbut when dealing with it .. you run into some problem with \nthe stack.. \n\n\nTRIPLE FAULT:\n\n- This is some error that occurs when handling a double fault.\n- it is unrecoverable ...\n- leads to a complete hardware reset!",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hlg2hHJucwDXQ9RlcbEJO",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -6179.698881219457,
      "y": 855.1638680593367,
      "width": 739.4282064217159,
      "height": 464.4983742100635,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
